## MapView.renderSync() method

Redraws scene immediately

 Before using this method, set `synchronousRendering` to `true` in the \[\[MapViewOptions\]\]

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
renderSync(frameStartTime?: number): void;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  frameStartTime | number | Optional timestamp for start of frame. Default: \[\[PerformanceTimer.now()\]\] |

<b>Returns:</b>

void
